00:01:56.760 --> 00:01:58.740
there's a settle point.

00:01:59.900 --> 00:02:01.760
And actually you can see them on the contour plot.

00:02:01.920 --> 00:02:04.220
On the contour plot, you see the maxima

00:02:04.220 --> 00:02:09.800
because the level curves become circles that now down

00:02:09.800 --> 00:02:12.620
and shrink to the maximum.

00:02:13.320 --> 00:02:14.720
